snippet.title: Shadow of the Tomb Raider - The Price of Survival [NR]
snippet.description:
Return to the lush world of Shadow of the Tomb Raider and solve a mystery behind Lara Croft's greatest foe in "The Price of Survival" https://TombRaider.Games/lara-croft-95c32

Crack the private codes of Trinity's leader, defeat the elite soldiers standing in your way, and explore a tomb wreathed in a poisonous past.

Equip the new Hunter's Array outfit, a classic Trinity uniform making Lara's footsteps quieter. With the new Silent Sting pistol and suppressor, your enemies will never hear you coming.

Subscribe to our channel to keep up-to-date with all things Tomb Raider and Lara Croft: https://www.youtube.com/user/tombraider?sub_confirmation=1
